{
  "id": "cfe078aa-6f8c-4484-87a3-9c80bb36f071",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.84,
      "text": "Neo's playstyle, no question about it",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ネオ選手のお箱といっても構わないでしょう"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.84,
      "end": 5.02,
      "text": "Right, Corrin's neutral B is pretty tough to execute",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "そうですね、カムイNBあれ相当むずいんですけどね"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.02,
      "end": 8.5,
      "text": "Corrin's fair doesn't have particularly long hitstun",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "カムイの空中前って別にヒットストップ長いわけじゃないので"
    },
    {
      "start": 8.5,
      "end": 10.64,
      "text": "The confirm is really difficult",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "確認本当に難しいと思うんですけど"
    },
    {
      "start": 10.64,
      "end": 12.52,
      "text": "Neo rarely misses it",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ネオ選手はなかなか外さない"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.52,
      "end": 15.84,
      "text": "Right, if the neutral B doesn't charge perfectly",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "確かね、NBもちょうどよくホールドしないと"
    },
    {
      "start": 15.84,
      "end": 17.44,
      "text": "The bite won't connect from the projectile",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "噛みつきが繋がらないはずで弾から"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.44,
      "end": 22.18,
      "text": "I've heard it's an insanely tight combo",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "相当シビアなコンボだっていうことは伺ったことがあるんです"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.18,
      "end": 25.58,
      "text": "Yeah, the opponent who got KO'd was Shuuton",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "はい、倒した相手はシュートン"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.58,
      "end": 28.76,
      "text": "At game count 1-1, he hits it with that momentum",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ゲームカウント1対1というこの状況で決めてくる弾力"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.76,
      "end": 31.64,
      "text": "And the execution precision",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "そして操作精度"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.64,
      "end": 39.58,
      "text": "Corrin denying the approach",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "カムイ 密着を拒否しつつ"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.58,
      "end": 43.38,
      "text": "Got through the punish",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "対処なり通りました"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.38,
      "end": 47.58,
      "text": "The playstyle's becoming more aggressive now",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "攻撃的な色になってきましたね"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.58,
      "end": 51.54,
      "text": "Purple, purple, yellow - that's the pattern",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "紫紫黄色という隊列です"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.54,
      "end": 54.94,
      "text": "Man, getting hit by this throw here is rough",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "いやーここの紫投擲が食らうのはちょっときついか"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.96,
      "end": 57.74,
      "text": "The knockback is key",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "唯一ね、あのノックバックがある"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.74,
      "end": 59.7,
      "text": "It is a throw though",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "紫投げではあるんですが"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.7,
      "end": 61.74,
      "text": "Into the air",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "空中へ"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.74,
      "end": 64.56,
      "text": "Continuing the pressure now",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "さあ展開を続けようというところ"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.56,
      "end": 65.56,
      "text": "Because of the situation",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "クエの内だから"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.56,
      "end": 68.6,
      "text": "Mashing out",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "暴れて"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.6,
      "end": 73.08,
      "text": "Hard to drop platform here but",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ここは台から降りにくい状況だが"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.08,
      "end": 74.5,
      "text": "Creates the gap nicely",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "うまく隙を作りました"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.5,
      "end": 77.98,
      "text": "Still it's tough",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "さあそれでも苦しい"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.98,
      "end": 79.62,
      "text": "Shuuton closed the line but",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ラインは詰めたのがシュートなんだが"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.62,
      "end": 81.22,
      "text": "Turned it right back around",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ここでうまく折り返していきました"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.22,
      "end": 84.16,
      "text": "That throw is doing work",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "紫投げがいい仕事をしている"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.16,
      "end": 85.02,
      "text": "Recovery...",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "復帰は"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.02,
      "end": 86.34,
      "text": "Not getting through",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "通さない"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.34,
      "end": 87.72,
      "text": "Even without a meteor",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "メテオじゃなくても結構"
